{
  "scenario_name": "11_telecom_core",
  "description": "Large-scale telecom core network with 40 hosts: AAA cluster (radius x3 + ldap master+slave), DNS cluster (2 primaries + 2 secondaries + resolver), VoIP cluster (sip_proxy x2 + media_gateway x2 + voip_pbx), Network Management (nms + ems + performance_mgmt + config_mgmt), Billing cluster (master + slave + mediation + rating_engine + cdr_server), OSS/BSS (service_fulfillment + trouble_ticketing + inventory_mgmt), Infrastructure (ntp x2 + syslog x2 + firewall_mgmt + monitoring x2 + backup x2), Core network (bgp_router x2 + mpls_controller + customer_portal). Exercises all 7 hardening actions: 3 turnoff_safely cases (ftp vulnerable on radius_secondary/mediation/backup), 3 reuse_service cases (netbios on ldap_slave/dns_secondary1/cdr_server), 2 patch_with_attention cases (https/billing_master and postgresql/syslog1), 2 patch_service cases (smb/ntp_server1 and kibana/monitoring1), and broad migrate_service/disable_service coverage.",
